    title: "Light and Shadow: A Visual Journey",
    excerpt:
      "Understanding how the interplay of light and shadow can create compelling visual narratives.",
    date: "Jan 14, 2024",
    author: "James Wilson",
    image:
      "https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/hobi.jpg-fzae4IjVr2MPfrjwvspsmgQwg6i07D.jpeg",
  },
  {
