    excerpt:
      "Why less is more: exploring minimalist approaches in modern photography.",
    date: "Jan 11, 2024",
    author: "Lisa Anderson",
    image:
      "https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/jimin.jpg-b7Ds4nMJajBwPEVpFmsN4hbd0ibZiD.jpeg",
